      "type": "text",
      "x": -14863.331301085083,
      "y": -3591.666411030772,
      "width": 1308.895690917968,
      "height": 540,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bIu",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 775299827,
      "version": 251,
      "versionNonce": 992840637,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772953495669,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Properties: Properties are the aspects of the selected elements you\nwant to style (like color, width, height, etc.).\n\ncolor: Defines the text color.\n\nbackground-color: Defines the background color of an element.\n\nfont-size: Sets the size of the font.\n\nmargin: Specifies the space around an element.\n\npadding: Defines the space between the element's content and its border.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Properties: Properties are the aspects of the selected elements you want to style (like color, width, height, etc.).\n\ncolor: Defines the text color.\n\nbackground-color: Defines the background color of an element.\n\nfont-size: Sets the size of the font.\n\nmargin: Specifies the space around an element.\n\npadding: Defines the space between the element's content and its border.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "x_eJO-20mlhXrgxjkE19Q",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -14871.703340880005,
      "y": -2987.666411030772,
      "width": 1291.6397705078134,
      "height": 90,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bIv",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1391412541,
      "version": 332,
      "versionNonce": 297109213,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772953528594,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. Values: Values define the specifics of the property you want to apply,\nsuch as a color name, a number (e.g., 16px), or percentages (e.g., 50%).",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Values: Values define the specifics of the property you want to apply, such as a color name, a number (e.g., 16px), or percentages (e.g., 50%).",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
