      "updated": 1775366992251,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "AUTOCOMMIT, COMMIT, ROLLBACK\n\nTransactions let you group operations and undo them if something goes wrong. AUTOCOMMIT saves changes immediately by\ndefault.\n\nSET AUTOCOMMIT = OFF;   -- disable auto-save\n\nSTART TRANSACTION;\nDELETE FROM students WHERE gpa < 2.0;\n-- Oops, wrong query?\nROLLBACK;               -- undo everything\n-- Or:\nCOMMIT;                 -- save permanently",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "AUTOCOMMIT, COMMIT, ROLLBACK\n\nTransactions let you group operations and undo them if something goes wrong. AUTOCOMMIT saves changes immediately by default.\n\nSET AUTOCOMMIT = OFF;   -- disable auto-save\n\nSTART TRANSACTION;\nDELETE FROM students WHERE gpa < 2.0;\n-- Oops, wrong query?\nROLLBACK;               -- undo everything\n-- Or:\nCOMMIT;                 -- save permanently",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
