      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CURRENT_DATE() & CURRENT_TIME()\n\nBuilt-in functions that return today's date and current time from the server.\n\nSELECT CURRENT_DATE();   -- e.g. 2026-04-04\nSELECT CURRENT_TIME();   -- e.g. 14:32:08\nSELECT NOW();            -- date + time together\n\n-- Use in INSERT\nINSERT INTO logs(event, logged_at)\nVALUES ('Login', NOW());",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CURRENT_DATE() & CURRENT_TIME()\n\nBuilt-in functions that return today's date and current time from the server.\n\nSELECT CURRENT_DATE();   -- e.g. 2026-04-04\nSELECT CURRENT_TIME();   -- e.g. 14:32:08\nSELECT NOW();            -- date + time together\n\n-- Use in INSERT\nINSERT INTO logs(event, logged_at)\nVALUES ('Login', NOW());",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
